OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChristmas 'spoilt' after   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftree removed every night   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, People living in a block of flats said 
OL,6, Christmas had been spoilt as they      
OL,7, cannot have a plastic tree in their    
OL,8, foyer unless a caretaker is present.   
OL,10,FHousing association BPHA told residents
OL,11,Fin Boswell Court, Bedford, they were   
OL,12,Ffollowing advice of the fire service.  
OL,14,FBedfordshire Fire and Rescue denied    
OL,15,Fissuing this advice.                   
OL,17,FA spokeswoman for BPHA said communal   
OL,18,Fareas in high rise blocks were kept    
OL,19,Fclear to avoid obstruction in the event
OL,20,Fof a fire.                             
